Coverage


December  7, 2015
2nd Circ. Says Harbinger’s $2B Suit Against GPS Cos. Fails
The Second Circuit on Monday upheld a decision dismissing Harbinger Capital Partners LLC’s $1.9 billion suit claiming three GPS makers hid market information and drove its startup LightSquared Inc. into bankruptcy, finding a lack of a relationship between the companies and the hedge fund.


